## ğŸ§® Key Metrics
- **Pass/Fail Rule** â†’ Students with 5+ Cs are considered to have passed.  
- **Grade Point Average (GPA)** â†’ Quality measure of passes.  
- **Pass Rate %** â†’ % of students meeting the 5C+ benchmark.  
- **Subject vs School Gap** â†’ How each subject compares to school average.  
- **Attendance Rate %** â†’ Student engagement metric.  

